updated_at: "2026-07-11T06:31:12.019Z"
assignee: codex-root
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 60
acceptance_criteria: suggested_retry consults the active extension/SDK command contract for flag arity; boolean extension flags render bare (--allow-empty) while value-taking extension flags keep the placeholder; repro from GH-507 (todos sync guard failure) yields a suggestion that succeeds verbatim; regression test covers boolean + value extension flags; GH-507 closed with a comment linking the fix
risk: low
confidence: high
